    <div class="container">
        <h1>PopDo Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="update-date">Last Updated: February 23, 2026</p>

        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>PopDo</strong> values your privacy above all else. This app does not store your to-do data on any
                server; all information is kept securely only within your device.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>1. Personal Information Collection</h2>
        <p>PopDo does not collect any direct personal information (such as name, email, or phone number) from users.
            However, the following information may be used to provide the service:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>To-Do Data</strong>: Titles, notes, and images (optional) entered by the user. This data is
                stored only on the user's device.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information</strong>: Anonymized log data used for bug fixes and app performance
                improvements.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Advertising and Analytics Services</h2>
        <p>This app uses third-party services for appropriate advertising and service analysis:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Google AdMob</strong>: May use device advertising IDs to display ads. (<a
                    href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Purpose of App Permissions</h2>
        <p>We request the following permissions to provide and optimize our features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Display over other apps (SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW)</strong>: Used to display the popup-style to-do
                list on the screen.</li>
            <li><strong>Run in the background (FOREGROUND_SERVICE)</strong>: Used to reliably display the to-do list on
                the lock screen.</li>
            <li><strong>Notifications (POST_NOTIFICATIONS)</strong>: Used for to-do alerts and schedule management.</li>
            <li><strong>Storage/Photos (IMAGE_PICKER)</strong>: Used to attach photos to to-do items.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Storage and Deletion</h2>
        <p>All to-do data generated in PopDo is stored only on the user's device (Shared Preferences/Local Storage). If
            the user deletes the app, all data stored on the device will also be deleted.</p>

        <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>PopDo does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding this policy or the use of the service, please contact us at:</p>
